name: DIE-MONDE moose
description:
Giclee Print of original oil on canvas painting.

Giclee prints are made using the latest Epson professional inkjets and printed on Hahnemuhle German Etching paper, a 310g.s.m. heavyweight etching board that’s silky smooth with a fine surface texture. It is one of the most popular media worldwide for artwork printing and allows a spot on representation of the original.

Prices include postage and packaging under Royal mail 1st class delivery. You will receive your print in a protective flat envelope or for sizes A3 and above in a roll tube.
